  "texts": [
    "Using GPT-4 as a calibrated rater under a fixed rubric proved useful for distinguishing between models.",
    "However, like other LLM-as-judge settings, it remains sensitive to prompt design and length effects [31].",
    "Complementing this approach with TOPSIS helped make explicit the assumptions behind weighting choices and showed how rankings can shift depending on the balance of dimensions considered.",
    "Our study also has several limitations that should be noted.",
    "The evaluation was based on a relatively small sample of reports, which restricts generalizability."
